The paper discusses the use of neural nets in reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces two new input transformation methods, which are likely to be of interest to researchers in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the application of these methods in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
